WEBVTT

00:01.130 --> 00:02.563
PREVIOUSLY
ON "VERONICA MARS"...

00:02.570 --> 00:04.219
IT WENT STRAIGHT OFF THE CLIFF!
THEY'RE ALL DEAD!

00:04.230 --> 00:05.629
THIS ISN'T YOUR FAULT.

00:05.630 --> 00:08.064
IF IT WASN'T FOR ME,
MEG WOULD HAVE BEEN IN THE LIMO.

00:08.070 --> 00:09.332
SHE WOULDN'T NEED
A MACHINE TO BREATHE.

00:09.340 --> 00:10.762
YOU MET JACKIE, RIGHT?

00:10.770 --> 00:12.271
Veronica: I DIDN'T REALIZE
YOU WERE LUNCH BUDDIES.

00:12.280 --> 00:14.077
I LIKE HER, OKAY?

00:14.080 --> 00:16.548
HEY, JACKIE...
AND RANDOM DUDE.

00:16.550 --> 00:19.474
THIS IS VERONICA, THE GIRL
I WAS A TOTAL BIATCH TO.

00:20.280 --> 00:21.918
HEY, CHECK THIS OUT.

00:21.920 --> 00:23.512
MR. DAVID "CURLY" MORAN.

00:23.520 --> 00:25.078
YOU'VE NEVER
SEEN HIM BEFORE?

00:25.090 --> 00:27.012
Veronica:
I HAVE SEEN THIS MAN BEFORE.

00:27.020 --> 00:30.080
WHY WOULD THIS MAN HAVE MY NAME
MAGIC-MARKERED ACROSS HIS HAND?

00:30.090 --> 00:32.752
WHAT WAS IT AARON WROTE
TO CURLY ON THAT PICTURE?

00:32.760 --> 00:35.024
"ALL TH ESE YEARS
STILL ON 'THE LONG HAUL,'

00:35.030 --> 00:38.488
FEATURING A STUNT PERFORMED
BY DAVID 'CURLY' MORAN."

00:38.500 --> 00:41.992
THE BUS CRASH --
IT WAS MEANT FOR ME.

00:42.000 --> 00:44.036
Man: HEY, CHER!

00:44.040 --> 00:45.598
YOU KNOW THAT GUY?

00:45.610 --> 00:46.679
NO.

00:51.480 --> 00:55.246
HI, CAN YOU TELL ME
IF MEG MANNING HAS BEEN MOVED

00:55.250 --> 00:58.788
FROM THE INTENSIVE CARE UNIT?

00:58.790 --> 01:01.111
AND WHAT ARE THE VISITING HOURS?

01:02.930 --> 01:04.227
THANK YOU.

01:05.760 --> 01:06.920
CAN I HELP YOU?

01:06.930 --> 01:08.727
I NEED TO HIRE
A DETECTIVE.

01:08.730 --> 01:12.598
RIGHT PLACE, WRONG DAY --
WE'RE NOT OPEN ON SUNDAYS.

01:12.600 --> 01:14.568
THIS IS KIND OF
AN EMERGENCY.

01:14.570 --> 01:16.936
I NEED TO INVESTIGATE
MY BOYFRIEND --

01:16.940 --> 01:18.828
OR, I GUESS,
MY POTENTIAL FIANC,

01:18.840 --> 01:22.071
NOW THAT I FOUND AN
ENGAGEMENT RING IN HIS GYM BAG.

01:22.080 --> 01:25.072
YOU FOUND IT IN HIS...?

01:25.080 --> 01:27.139
I NEED SOME SERIOUS,
SERIOUS ANSWERS.

01:27.150 --> 01:29.345
I CAN TAKE DOWN
YOUR INFORMATION

01:29.350 --> 01:32.217
AND MAKE SURE
MR. MARS GETS IT FIRST THING.

01:32.220 --> 01:34.154
HIS NAME IS COLLIN NEVIN.

01:34.160 --> 01:35.616
OKEYDOKEY.

01:35.620 --> 01:38.259
START WITH THE BASICS --
OUR STANDARD PACKAGE,

01:38.260 --> 01:40.353
YOUR GARDEN-VARIETY
BACKGROUND CHECK,

01:40.360 --> 01:42.362
CRIMINAL RECORD, ALIASES.

01:42.370 --> 01:43.723
I NEED WAY MORE
THAN THAT.

01:43.730 --> 01:45.561
WELL, THERE'S
OUR PREMIUM PACKAGE --

01:45.570 --> 01:48.095
MR. MARS WILL "GET TO KNOW"
A FEW FRIENDS,

01:48.100 --> 01:50.102
CHAT UP AN EX OR TWO.

01:50.110 --> 01:52.101
WHICH IS WHAT I'M AFRAID
COLLIN'S DOING.

01:52.110 --> 01:54.829
LOOK, COLLIN LIVES OFF
A TRUST FUND.

01:54.840 --> 01:56.501
HE HAS A LOT OF FREE TIME.

01:56.510 --> 01:59.172
I'D LIKE TO KNOW
HOW HE SPENDS IT.

01:59.180 --> 02:00.909
WELL, THERE IS
OUR SILVER PACKAGE.

02:00.920 --> 02:02.512
WHAT'S THE SILVER PACKAGE?

02:02.520 --> 02:04.511
PREMIUM PACKAGE
PLUS SURVEILLANCE --

02:04.520 --> 02:06.454
PHONE RECORDS,
E-MAIL MONITORING.

02:06.460 --> 02:08.382
IT'S BASICALLY
AN ALL-ACCESS PASS

02:08.390 --> 02:10.858
TO WHAT HE'S DOING
WHEN YOU'RE NOT LOOKING.

02:10.860 --> 02:11.986
I'LL TAKE IT.

02:11.990 --> 02:13.093
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

02:13.100 --> 02:15.091
OH. [ CHUCKLES ]

02:15.100 --> 02:16.567
IT'S HIM.

02:17.800 --> 02:19.768
HE THINKS I'M AT YOGA.

02:20.870 --> 02:22.269
GREAT.

02:22.270 --> 02:25.398
WELL, MR. MARS WILL
REVIEW YOUR CASE, MS. BLOCK,

02:25.410 --> 02:27.401
AND HE'LL BE IN TOUCH
TOMORROW.

02:27.410 --> 02:29.901
AH, THE MAN OF THE HOUR.
KEITH MARS, JULIE BLOCK.

02:29.910 --> 02:32.105
LOOKING FORWARD
TO WORKING WITH YOU.

02:32.110 --> 02:33.509
HUH.

02:33.520 --> 02:35.249
NICE.

02:35.250 --> 02:36.808
JUMPY FIANC?

02:36.820 --> 02:39.789
JUMPY POTENTIAL FIANC,
WITH CASH TO BURN.

02:39.790 --> 02:42.679
SHE PRACTICALLY HANDED ME
A BLANK CHECK.

02:42.690 --> 02:45.056
YOU'RE ORGANIZING THE OFFICE,
NOT SOLICITING CLIENTS.

02:45.060 --> 02:47.528
MAYBE YOU HAVEN'T NOTICED
I'M RUNNING FOR SHERIFF.

02:47.530 --> 02:49.623
I CAN'T EVEN GET TO THE CASES
I ALREADY HAVE.

02:49.630 --> 02:52.292
MAYBE I COULD HELP --
JUST WITH THE LITTLE STUFF,

02:52.300 --> 02:53.938
NOTHING THAT REQUIRES
BODY ARMOR.

02:53.940 --> 02:56.704
YOU DON'T WORK HERE.
YOU WORK AT JAVA THE HUT.

02:56.710 --> 03:00.032
YEAH, THAT TIP MONEY'S
GONNA PAY FOR STANFORD.

03:00.040 --> 03:01.678
NO.

03:01.680 --> 03:04.706
BUT THE KANE SCHOLARSHIP WILL,
SO USE YOUR NIGHTS TO STUDY.

03:04.710 --> 03:08.544
PLEASE, CALL MISS JUMPY AND
TELL HER I CAN'T TAKE THIS CASE.

03:10.150 --> 03:12.414
[ SIGHS ]

03:12.420 --> 03:15.787
[ DIALING ]

03:15.790 --> 03:19.851
JULIE, HI. IT'S VERONICA
FROM MARS INVESTIGATIONS.

03:19.860 --> 03:21.191
I'M REALLY SORRY,

03:21.200 --> 03:24.988
BUT MR. MARS IS UNABLE TO TAKE
ON ANY NEW CASES AT THIS TIME.

03:25.000 --> 03:26.729
RECOMMENDATION?

03:26.740 --> 03:30.335
UH, NICK HARRIS DETECT IVES
IS ALWAYS GOOD.

03:30.340 --> 03:31.659
IF YOU'RE LOOKING LOCALLY,

03:31.670 --> 03:35.071
VINNIE VAN LOWE
IS A RESPECT ED DETECTIVE.

03:35.080 --> 03:38.379
[ Dial tone ]
I'M REALLY SORRY
ABOUT THIS, JULIE.

03:38.380 --> 03:40.974
I HOPE IT ALL WORKS OUT.
WE WISH YOU THE BEST.

03:43.490 --> 03:46.209
THE ONLY WAY I'D EVER MAKE
2 GRAND IN A WEEK

03:46.220 --> 03:49.109
WORKING AT THE HUT
IS IF THEY INSTALLED A POLE.

03:49.120 --> 03:51.850
DAD MIGHT BE TOO BUSY
FOR MISS BRIGHT-SIDE,

03:51.860 --> 03:55.956
BUT I CAN PENCIL IN SOME TIME
TO MAKE A COUPLE QUICK G's.

03:57.900 --> 04:01.358
MR. MARS THOUGHT THAT,
DUE TO THE NATURE OF YOUR CASE,

04:01.370 --> 04:02.803
IT MIGHT BE BENEFICIAL

04:02.810 --> 04:05.859
FOR YOU TO HAVE A DETECTIVE
OF THE FEMALE PERSUASION.

04:05.870 --> 04:08.600
AREN'T YOU AWFULLY YOUNG
TO BE DOING THIS?

04:08.610 --> 04:11.499
IT'S AMAZING -- I NEVER
GET TIRED OF THAT QUESTION.

04:11.510 --> 04:15.571
JULIE, WHY DO YOU SUSPECT
THAT COLLIN IS UP TO SOMETHING?

04:15.580 --> 04:19.243
MY FAMILY IS WEALTHY --
LIKE VERY.

04:19.250 --> 04:21.013
I TEND TO FALL FOR GUYS

04:21.020 --> 04:23.557
WHO NAIL THE GIRL
WHO'S TEACHING MY SPIN CLASS

04:23.560 --> 04:25.551
WHILE LETTING ME
PAY HIS RENT.

04:27.360 --> 04:28.998
MONEY ISN'T
SUPPOSED TO MATTER,

04:29.000 --> 04:32.128
SO I'M LETTING COLLIN THINK
I'M REGULAR OLD MIDDLE CLASS.

04:32.130 --> 04:33.392
I SEE.

04:33.400 --> 04:34.799
WELL, IS THERE SOMETHING

04:34.800 --> 04:37.462
THAT'S PROMPTING YOUR CONCERN
RIGHT NOW?

04:37.470 --> 04:39.802
PHONE CALLS AT LATE HOURS,

04:39.810 --> 04:42.540
LAME EXCUSES FOR GETTING
OUT OF THE HOUSE.

04:42.550 --> 04:44.643
LATELY, IT'S TENNIS.

04:44.650 --> 04:49.110
THERE IS A FRAMED PHOTO
OF A WOMAN ON HIS BAR.

04:49.120 --> 04:50.542
OKAY.

04:50.550 --> 04:52.950
UH, GOT IT.
I'M ON IT.

04:52.960 --> 04:54.518
THAN KS.

04:54.520 --> 04:58.684
WALLACE? DO YOU HAVE A SHIFT
AT SAC-N-PAC TONIGHT?

04:58.690 --> 04:59.952
NOPE.

04:59.960 --> 05:02.565
HOTTEST GIRL IN SCHOOL ASKED ME
FOR HELP WITH TRIG.

05:02.570 --> 05:04.162
I'M GONNA GIVE HER A HAND.

05:04.170 --> 05:05.967
YOU NEED HELP WITH TRIG.

05:05.970 --> 05:09.098
IN FACT, I MIGHT GIVE HER
BOTH HANDS.

05:09.100 --> 05:11.136
ARE YOU HITTIN' THAT?

05:11.140 --> 05:12.402
OOH-HOO-HOO!

05:12.410 --> 05:14.799
[ Laughing ] DARRELL!

05:17.710 --> 05:19.940
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

05:22.250 --> 05:24.548
[ CAR DEPARTS ]

05:36.230 --> 05:40.189
* A LONG TIME AGO,
WE USED TO BE FRIENDS *

05:40.200 --> 05:45.536
* BUT I HAVEN'T THOUGHT OF YOU
LATELY AT ALL *

05:46.410 --> 05:48.537
* COME ON, NOW, SUGAR *

05:48.540 --> 05:50.747
* BRING IT ON, BRING IT ON,
YEAH *

05:50.750 --> 05:54.618
* JUST REMEMBER ME WHEN *

05:54.620 --> 05:59.341
* WE USED TO BE FRIENDS
A LONG TIME AGO *

05:59.350 --> 06:01.853
* WE USED TO BE FRIENDS *

06:09.100 --> 06:10.863
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

06:14.540 --> 06:17.065
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING ]

06:21.440 --> 06:23.670
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

06:26.880 --> 06:27.972
HI, JULIE.

06:27.980 --> 06:29.242
Find out anything?

06:29.250 --> 06:30.649
YOU CAN REST EASY.

06:30.650 --> 06:32.379
He's on his eighth lap.

06:32.390 --> 06:34.711
and I'm on my way to Starbucks,

06:34.720 --> 06:36.119
'CAUSE I GOTTA SAY --

06:36.120 --> 06:38.782
SPYING ON COLLIN --
LITTLE BORING.

06:38.790 --> 06:40.826
I LOOKED UP
HIS CALLER I.D. HISTORY.

06:40.830 --> 06:44.061
HE'S HAD 20 CALLS IN THE PAST
6 DAYS FROM THE SAME NUMBER.

06:44.070 --> 06:45.367
DON'T YOU THINK THAT'S ODD?

06:45.370 --> 06:48.191
It's worth looking into.
What's the number? 1'” --

06:48.200 --> 06:49.565
I ALREADY SENT IT TO YOU.

06:49.570 --> 06:51.663
Don't forget --
tomorrow he has tennis.

06:51.670 --> 06:53.900
Alicia: KNOCK, KNOCK!

06:55.740 --> 06:58.641
TELL ME THAT'S
A HAM AND CHEESE SANDWICH.

06:58.650 --> 07:01.312
AND I ALMOST WENT
FOR THE CHICKEN SALAD.

07:01.320 --> 07:05.484
OH, YOU JUST FULFILLED ONE OF
THE TOP-10 MALE FANTASIES.

07:05.490 --> 07:07.617
OH, YEAH, A GUY DREAMS
HIS WHOLE LIFE

07:07.620 --> 07:10.418
OF A BEAUTIFUL WOMAN
BRINGING HIM A SANDWICH.

07:15.230 --> 07:16.788
MMM.

07:18.600 --> 07:20.739
DO YOU HAVE A SPARE GUN
I COULD BORROW?

07:24.310 --> 07:26.801
THAT DEPENDS.

07:26.810 --> 07:29.233
WHO DO YOU INTEND TO SHOOT?

07:29.240 --> 07:31.071
THE GUY
WHO CALLED OUT TO ME

07:31.080 --> 07:33.810
IN THE CLUB IN CHICAGO --
"CHER."

07:35.120 --> 07:36.439
HE WAS MY OLD BOYFRIEND,

07:36.450 --> 07:38.145
AND "CHER" WAS
HIS NICKNAME FOR ME.

07:38.150 --> 07:40.459
WHEN WE WERE IN CHICAGO,
I ASKED YOU --

07:40.460 --> 07:43.258
I KNOW. HE CAUGHT ME
COMPLETELY OFF GUARD.

07:43.260 --> 07:46.491
WE DATED ALMOST 20 YEARS AGO,
BEFORE I WAS MARRIED.

07:46.500 --> 07:49.424
AND I WAS YOUNG
AND NAIVE...

07:49.430 --> 07:50.920
AND HE WAS CRAZY.

07:50.930 --> 07:52.989
SO, WHERE DOES THE GUN PART
COME IN?

07:53.000 --> 07:55.889
HE DROVE BY MY HOUSE
YESTERDAY MORNING.

07:57.370 --> 07:59.133
HE'S TRACKED ME DOWN.

07:59.140 --> 08:00.835
THERE'S NO WAY
I'M LETTING YOU

08:00.840 --> 08:02.842
TAKE A GUN
YOU DON'T KNOW HOW TO HANDLE

08:02.850 --> 08:04.545
TO A HOUSE
WITH A 7-YEAR-OLD.

08:04.550 --> 08:06.472
SO I'LL GIVE YOU SOMETHING
A LITTLE SAFER

08:06.480 --> 08:08.869
TO CURL UP WITH AT NIGHT.

08:08.880 --> 08:10.188
WHAT?

08:11.290 --> 08:12.279
YOU?

08:12.290 --> 08:14.019
[ CHUCKLES ]

08:15.890 --> 08:18.427
WHAT DO WE TELL THE KIDS?

08:18.430 --> 08:20.819
NOTHING.

08:23.370 --> 08:25.691
I THINK I COOKED THESE
TOO FAST.

08:25.700 --> 08:28.635
I GOT A LATE START
THIS MORNING.

08:28.640 --> 08:30.232
MOM, YOU OKAY?
UH-HUH.

08:30.240 --> 08:33.038
WHY DON'T YOU JUST
SIT DOWN AND EAT?

08:33.040 --> 08:34.234
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

08:34.240 --> 08:35.502
OH.

08:35.510 --> 08:37.375
NICE SURPRISE.

08:37.380 --> 08:38.699
GOOD MERNING.

08:38.710 --> 08:41.440
I WAS OUT EARLY
DOING SOME SURVEILLANCE.

08:41.450 --> 08:43.247
THOUGHT I'D STOP BY,
SAY HI,

08:43.250 --> 08:45.718
AND SEND THE FENNEL MEN
TO SCHOOL

08:45.720 --> 08:47.881
WITH A BELLYFUL OF SUGAR.

08:47.890 --> 08:49.585
MMM.

08:49.590 --> 08:51.478
KEITH MARS FOR SHERIFF.

08:51.490 --> 08:52.798
[ CHUCKLES ]

08:55.130 --> 08:57.360
MY DAD SPEND THE NIGHT
AT YOUR PLACE?

08:57.370 --> 08:58.519
YEP.

08:58.530 --> 09:01.033
HE DO THE A.M. DOUGHNUT
FAKE-OUT RUN?

09:01.040 --> 09:02.860
WANT ONE?

09:04.240 --> 09:05.207
[ LAUGHS ]

09:05.210 --> 09:07.007
GET BACK, LADIES --
HE'S MINE!

09:07.010 --> 09:10.002
YOU REALLY ARE
A BASKETBALL STAR, AREN'T YOU?

09:10.010 --> 09:13.741
I'M NOT SMACKING THE ASS
OF SOME DUNGEONS & DRAGONS GEEK?

09:13.750 --> 09:16.446
OH, HE'S A STAR.
JUST ASK HIM.

09:16.450 --> 09:18.680
COME ON. LET'S GO.

09:25.630 --> 09:28.019
[ TWIGS SNAP ]

09:41.110 --> 09:43.101
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING ]
SMILE!

09:43.110 --> 09:46.238
OH, YEAH, WORK IT!
WORK IT!

09:46.250 --> 09:48.514
YOU'RE GONNA BE PULLING
THAT CAMERA OUT YOUR --

09:48.520 --> 09:50.181
UNH-UNH.

09:50.190 --> 09:53.353
THE LIGHT'S MUCH BETTER
WHERE YOU'RE STANDING.

09:53.360 --> 09:55.009
KEITH MARS --

09:55.020 --> 09:59.127
FORMER SHERIFF,
PRIVATE DETECTIVE, AUTHOR.

09:59.130 --> 10:00.620
WOW.

10:00.630 --> 10:02.257
CARL MORGAN --

10:02.260 --> 10:05.195
THREE YEARS LOMPOC,
ASSAULT AND BATTERY,

10:05.200 --> 10:07.896
COCAINE POSSESSION,
INTENT TO SELL.

10:07.900 --> 10:10.903
WE SHOULD REALLY GIVE
OUR PUBLICISTS PATS ON THE BACK.

10:10.910 --> 10:13.538
I EXPECTED YOU TO BECOME
A PROBLEM AT SOME POINT.

10:13.540 --> 10:17.374
THERE'S A FLIGHT TO CHICAGO
LEAVING SAN DIEGO AT 4:45.

10:17.380 --> 10:18.938
YOU NEED TO BE ON IT.

10:18.950 --> 10:21.544
THE NEXT TIME I SHOOT YOU,
IT WON'T BE DIGITALLY.

10:21.550 --> 10:25.111
UNLESS I HIT YOU IN THE FINGER.
THEN WE'LL LAUGH ABOUT IT.

10:25.120 --> 10:27.179
[ LAUGHS ]

10:27.190 --> 10:30.626
YOUR OLD LADY
TOOK SOMETHING OF MINE.

10:30.630 --> 10:34.225
I'M NOT LEAVING
TILL I GET IT BACK.

10:34.230 --> 10:36.152
SHE'S NOT MY OLD LADY.

10:36.160 --> 10:39.835
SHE'S MY SPECIAL
LADY FRIEND.

10:45.310 --> 10:49.371
HOSPITALS WIG ME OUT, BUT
I'VE PUT THIS OFF FOR TOO LONG.

10:49.380 --> 10:52.304
IT'S TIME I SEE MEG.

10:52.310 --> 10:53.447
VERONICA?

10:53.450 --> 10:55.077
DUNCAN?

10:56.580 --> 10:59.515
I DIDN'T KNOW YOU WERE --

10:59.520 --> 11:00.817
HOW'S MEG?

11:00.820 --> 11:02.959
[ DOOR OPENS ]

11:05.330 --> 11:06.854
YOU AGAIN?

11:06.860 --> 11:09.328
WHY DO YOU COME HERE
EVERY DAY?

11:09.330 --> 11:11.628
HOW MANY TIMES
DO I HAVE TO TELL YOU?

11:11.630 --> 11:13.996
WE NEVER WANT TO SEE YOU AGAIN!
STAY AWAY FROM OUR DAUGHTER!

11:14.000 --> 11:17.128
AND YOU -- I MEAN,
HOW CAN YOU COME HERE?

11:17.140 --> 11:19.404
DON'T YOU KNOW YOUR PRESENCE
IS UPSETTING TO US?

11:19.410 --> 11:21.002
WE CARE ABOUT MEG.

11:21.010 --> 11:22.602
MOM, HE --
QUIET.

11:22.610 --> 11:24.840
IF YOU REALLY CARED
ABOUT MEG,

11:24.850 --> 11:28.013
SHE WOULDN'T HAVE BEEN
ON THAT BUS.

11:28.020 --> 11:31.387
Woman on P.A.:
DR. GODOT TO NURSE'S STATION 3.

11:31.390 --> 11:34.848
DR. GODOT
TO NURSE'S STATION 3.

11:37.160 --> 11:39.253
YOU DIDN'T TELL ME
ABOUT --

11:39.260 --> 11:41.922
WHAT? THAT MEG
WAS IMPORTANT TO ME?

11:41.930 --> 11:43.659
ABOUT HER PARENTS.

11:43.670 --> 11:45.888
DR. ROBERTS TO O.R. -- STAT.

11:45.900 --> 11:47.868
YOU WANT TO GO EAT
OR SOMETHING?

11:47.870 --> 11:49.633
CAN'T -- WORK.

11:49.640 --> 11:52.837
GOTTA GO WATCH
A TENNIS MATCH.

12:04.850 --> 12:07.489
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING ]

12:07.490 --> 12:10.186
Veronica: WELL,
THIS ISN'T A TENNIS COURT.

12:10.190 --> 12:12.920
WHAT ARE YOU UP TO, COLLIN?

12:12.930 --> 12:14.397
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING ]

12:20.070 --> 12:21.833
NO GOOD, IT APPEARS.

12:21.840 --> 12:23.432
WHAT IS IT WITH MEN?

12:23.440 --> 12:26.807
NEVER WHERE
YOU EXPECT THEM TO BE.

12:30.550 --> 12:32.973
[ COMPUTER BEEPING ]

12:32.980 --> 12:34.618
[ DIALING ]

12:34.620 --> 12:35.939
Julie: HELLO?

12:35.950 --> 12:38.942
JULIE, IT'S VERONICA.
CAN YOU CHECK YOUR E-MAIL?

12:38.950 --> 12:41.282
I'M SENDING YOU SOME PHOTOS
RIGHT NOW.

12:41.290 --> 12:46.387
AND DO YOU KNOW ANYONE
WHO LIVES AT 8520 PRIMROSE LANE?

12:46.390 --> 12:48.358
Julie: No. Why?

12:48.360 --> 12:50.965
I'M AFRAID
I'VE GOT SOME BAD NEWS

12:50.970 --> 12:52.494
AND SOME MORE BAD NEWS.

12:52.500 --> 12:55.435
FIRST, COLLIN'S NOT
PLAYING TENNIS.

12:55.440 --> 12:56.691
AND SECOND,

12:56.700 --> 12:59.703
THAT NUMBER THAT SHOWED UP
20 TIMES ON HIS CALLER I.D...

12:59.710 --> 13:01.200
Yeah?

13:01.210 --> 13:04.338
THAT NUMBER BELONGS TO WHOEVER
LIVES HERE ON PRIMROSE LANE.

13:04.350 --> 13:06.648
IT'S WHERE HE GOES
INSTEAD OF TENNIS.

13:06.650 --> 13:10.609
DID YOU GET THE PHOTO YET?
DO YOU RECOGNIZE THE WOMAN?

13:10.620 --> 13:11.746
Oh, no. Oh, no.

13:11.750 --> 13:12.819
JULIE --

13:12.820 --> 13:14.014
No, no, no. No.

13:14.020 --> 13:17.251
JULIE, LISTEN TO ME.
DO NOT PANIC, OKAY?

13:17.260 --> 13:20.752
I'LL CALL YOU
AS SOON AS I KNOW ANYTHING.

13:20.760 --> 13:21.795
OKAY?

13:21.800 --> 13:23.062
Okay.

13:23.070 --> 13:24.697
ALL RIGHT, BYE.

13:24.700 --> 13:26.395
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

13:31.940 --> 13:33.601
* JEALOUSY *

13:35.080 --> 13:37.241
* MY DEVIL *

13:37.250 --> 13:40.276
ALL RIGHT, COLLIN,
JUST GIVE ME WHAT I CAME FOR --

13:40.280 --> 13:43.784
YOU AND YOUR HOT LITTLE NUMBER,
DEEP IN THE THROES OF --

13:43.790 --> 13:45.587
[ SPEAKING HEBREW ]

13:45.590 --> 13:47.512
A HEBREW LESSON?

13:48.690 --> 13:51.921
* INSOMNIA *

13:51.930 --> 13:55.297
* JEALOUSY *

13:55.300 --> 13:56.597
[ TIRES SQUEAL ]

13:56.600 --> 13:57.589
RUH-ROH.

13:59.430 --> 14:01.330
JULIE, NO!

14:03.470 --> 14:04.607
OH!

14:04.610 --> 14:09.001
JULIE, STAND DOWN.
HE'S NOT CHEATING ON YOU.

14:09.010 --> 14:10.875
HE'S WITH A RABBI.

14:10.880 --> 14:12.279
A RABBI?

14:12.280 --> 14:15.169
HE'S NOT JEWISH!
I'M JEWISH!

14:17.520 --> 14:19.784
ARE YOU THERE YET?

14:19.850 --> 14:25.629
* AHHHH, AHHH-AHHH *

14:25.630 --> 14:28.098
* OHHHH *

14:28.100 --> 14:33.037
"EVERY DAY" --
THAT'S WHAT MEG'S DAD SAID.

14:33.040 --> 14:35.497
WHAT'S DUNCAN DOING
AT THE HOSPITAL?

14:35.500 --> 14:37.104
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

14:39.470 --> 14:40.607
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

14:40.610 --> 14:43.909
Julie: Do you think
he still loves her?

14:43.910 --> 14:45.639
I DON'T KNOW.

14:45.650 --> 14:47.572
WHAT? WHO IS THIS?

14:47.580 --> 14:50.515
IT'S JULIE. THE PHOTO
OF THE WOMAN ON THE BAR?

14:50.520 --> 14:52.442
She's got to be an ex.

14:52.450 --> 14:55.817
IF HE'S KEEPING HER CLOSE,
DO YOU THINK HE STILL LOVES HER?

14:55.820 --> 14:57.981
WHOA -- IF I'M PONDERING
THE SAME QUESTION

14:57.990 --> 15:00.595
ABOUT MY BOYFRIEND,
DOES THAT MAKE ME CRAZY, TOO?

15:00.600 --> 15:04.058
JULIE, IT'S 2:27
IN THE MORNING.

15:04.070 --> 15:06.129
The silver package
has its perks,

15:06.130 --> 15:08.837
BUT POST-MIDNIGHT GIRL TALK
IS NOT ONE OF THEM.

15:08.840 --> 15:11.934
WHAT IF I GET AN UPGRADE?
WHAT COMES AI-TER SILVER?

15:11.940 --> 15:12.929
PSYCHO.

15:12.940 --> 15:14.601
WHAT?
Gold.

15:14.610 --> 15:16.942
JULIE, IT'S $3,000.

15:16.950 --> 15:18.645
WHAT DOES IT INCLUDE?

15:18.650 --> 15:21.278
UH...WE DIG DEEPER.

15:21.280 --> 15:24.681
THREE MONTHS OF INTERNET
ACTIVITY, HEAVIER SURVEILLANCE.

15:24.690 --> 15:27.887
We talk to consultants _
to set up a temptation scenario

15:27.890 --> 15:30.188
AND SEE IF HE RESPONDS.

15:30.190 --> 15:31.452
THAT'S PERFECT.

15:31.460 --> 15:33.348
That's exactly
what I need.

15:33.360 --> 15:35.248
WITH THE GOLD PACKAGE,
CAN YOU FIND OUT

15:35.260 --> 15:37.069
WHO THAT IS
IN THE PHOTO ON THE BAR?

15:37.070 --> 15:38.822
WE CAN FIND OUT.

15:38.830 --> 15:41.367
BUT IF YOU WANT
MY OPINION,

15:41.370 --> 15:44.703
I'D SAY THERE'S A FINE LINE
BETWEEN LOOKING FOR A PROBLEM

15:44.710 --> 15:46.530
AND CREATING ONE.

15:46.540 --> 15:48.576
GOOD NIGHT.

15:48.580 --> 15:51.549
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

15:51.550 --> 15:52.972
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

15:52.980 --> 15:55.619
WHO LET YOU
INTO MY OFFICE?

15:55.620 --> 15:57.281
THAT'S FUNNY --
I WAS WONDERING THE SAME THING.

15:57.290 --> 16:00.851
I THOUGHT YOU MIGHT WANT
TO CATCH A BAD GUY OR SOMETHING.

16:00.860 --> 16:02.384
THAT'S CARL MORGAN,
DRUG DEALER.

16:02.390 --> 16:05.848
HE'S WANTED FOR QUESTIONING
IN CHICAGO ON AN ARMED ROBBERY.

16:05.860 --> 16:08.852
DRUG DEALER? FOR ME?

16:08.860 --> 16:10.122
IT'S NOT EVEN MY BIRTHDAY.

16:10.130 --> 16:12.166
HE'S BUDDIES
WITH A DEALER I'M TRACKING.

16:12.170 --> 16:14.388
THERE'S NO BOUNTY ON HIM,
NOTHING IN IT FOR ME.

16:14.400 --> 16:16.789
NOTHING BUT THE JOY
OF GIVING.

16:16.800 --> 16:19.132
IT'S NOT A PRESENT, SHERIFF.
IT'S KIND OF YOUR JOB.

16:19.140 --> 16:21.279
FOR NOW, ANYWAY.

16:26.950 --> 16:29.510
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

16:32.050 --> 16:34.257
YO, MARTHA.

16:34.260 --> 16:37.559
I HEAD YOU TOOK A RIDE DOWNTOWN
BEHIND THE 187.

16:37.560 --> 16:39.380
SO, DID YOU FLOP
FOR THE COPS

16:39.390 --> 16:42.689
OR DID THE LOCAL WAPNER HOOK YOU
UP WITH SOME ANKLE BLING?

16:42.700 --> 16:43.962
YOU KNOW THE DEAL, CUZ.

16:43.970 --> 16:46.165
EVERY TIME A KITTY CRIES
IN THIS TOWN,

16:46.170 --> 16:48.434
ONE-TIME TRIES
TO PUT A CASE ON ME.

16:48.440 --> 16:51.068
SPEAKING OF BLING,
WHAT'S UP WITH THE HOOPS?

16:51.070 --> 16:53.630
IF I RUB YOUR HEAD,
DO I GET THREE WISHES?

16:53.640 --> 16:54.937
YOU RUB MY HEAD,

16:54.940 --> 16:58.239
AND YOU MIGHT WANT TO MAKE
SEEING TOMORROW YOUR FIRST WISH.

17:00.650 --> 17:02.072
MISSING AN EARRING?

17:04.850 --> 17:06.784
YOU NEED TO BE ALONE
FOR A SECOND?

17:06.790 --> 17:09.611
WHERE'S THAT DISCO BALL
YOU USUALLY WEAR?

17:09.620 --> 17:10.780
[ CHUCKLES ]

17:10.790 --> 17:12.929
IT'S PROBABLY DEEP
IN SOME CHICK'S SHAG CARPET.

17:12.930 --> 17:14.989
YOU THINK?
YEAH.

17:15.000 --> 17:18.060
I'M GUESSING AN EVIDENCE BAG
IN THE SHERIFF'S OFFICE.

17:19.870 --> 17:21.394
OUT WITH YOU, DOG.

17:21.400 --> 17:23.800
MY QUESTION -- AND I'M BETTING
IT'S THE SHERIFF'S --

17:23.810 --> 17:26.301
WHAT WAS YOUR EARRING DOING
AT THE ROAD HOG

17:26.310 --> 17:28.676
IN THE LAST PLACE
CURLY MORAN WAS SEEN ALIVE?

17:28.680 --> 17:31.478
I DON'T EVEN KNOW WHAT EARRING
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT, SO --

17:31.480 --> 17:33.311
THE ONE YOU'RE WEARING
IN YOUR YEARBOOK PHOTO.

17:33.320 --> 17:35.811
HMM...SHERIFF'S DEPARTMENT,
SPEED DIAL --

17:35.820 --> 17:39.210
IF THIS DOESN'T GET ME
OUT OF THAT JAYWALKING TICKET...

17:39.220 --> 17:40.687
HELLO, INGA.

17:40.690 --> 17:42.009
OKAY.

17:42.020 --> 17:43.089
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

17:43.090 --> 17:44.557
A COUPLE WEEKS AGO,

17:44.560 --> 17:46.858
A FEW DAYS BEFORE CURLY BEACHED,
I GOT THIS WEIRD CALL --

17:46.860 --> 17:49.420
SOME GUY SAYING
CURLY WAS BEHIND THE BUS CRASH.

17:49.430 --> 17:50.863
YOU DON'T KNOW
WHO IT WAS?

17:50.870 --> 17:53.759
THEY JUST SAID CURLY WAS HIRED
BY THE FITZPATRICKS

17:53.770 --> 17:54.998
TO GET BACK AT CERVANDO.

17:55.000 --> 17:56.968
AS IN THE
"FIGHTING FITZPATRICKS"?

17:56.970 --> 17:58.403
UH-HUH.

17:58.410 --> 18:00.799
MY DAD PUT FIVE
OF THE FITZPATRICKS IN CHINO.

18:00.810 --> 18:02.175
THEY'RE IRISH CATHOLIC.

18:02.180 --> 18:04.705
FOR EVERY 5 YOU PUT AWAY,
THERE'S 10 MORE AT HOME.

18:04.710 --> 18:08.248
CERVANDO HAD BEEN BRAGGING ABOUT
HOW HE HUSTLED LEON FITZPATRICK

18:08.250 --> 18:10.411
OUT OF A FEW GRAND
DOWN AT RIVER STYX.

18:10.420 --> 18:12.911
THAT'S A LOT OF INFO
FOR AN ANONYMOUS CALL.

18:12.920 --> 18:14.148
WHAT'D YOU DO?

18:14.160 --> 18:15.411
NOTHING.
I'M SURE.

18:15.420 --> 18:16.978
THE FITZPATRICKS
ARE METH-HEAD LUNATICS,

18:16.990 --> 18:20.323
BUT THEY'RE NOT GONNA KILL A BUS
FULL OF KIDS OVER 3 GRAND.

18:20.330 --> 18:21.752
THEIR PROBLEM WITH CERVANDO

18:21.760 --> 18:24.729
WOULD HAVE BEEN SOLVED
IN AN ALLEY WITH A BASEBALL BAT.

18:24.730 --> 18:25.890
GIVE ME YOUR CELL.

18:25.900 --> 18:29.165
I CALLED THE MYSTERY GUY BACK.
ALL IT DOES IS RING.

18:29.800 --> 18:33.065
LOOK, SHOULD I BE EXPECTING
A VISIT FROM LAMB?

18:33.070 --> 18:36.278
IF I KNOW I'M BEING BROUGHT IN,
I'LL PUT ON GOOD UNDERWEAR.

18:36.280 --> 18:38.703
YOU SHOULD REALLY DO THAT
ANYWAY.

18:40.780 --> 18:42.816
[ ROBERT CRAY'S
"JEALOUS LOVE" PLAYS ]

18:42.820 --> 18:47.553
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]
* AND EVERY TIME
A PRETTY GIRL WALK BY *

18:47.560 --> 18:50.256
* I CATCH YOU
WATCHIN' ME, BABY *

18:50.260 --> 18:52.080
Veronica: Hey, buddy.
Whatcha doin'?

18:52.090 --> 18:55.298
VERONICA, ARE YOU IN IMMEDIATE,
LIFE-THREATENING DANGER?

18:55.300 --> 18:57.291
AT THIS PRECISE MOMENT, NO.

18:57.300 --> 18:59.165
THEN I'M HANGING UP.
Wait! Wait!

18:59.170 --> 19:01.092
My go-to temptress
just canceled on me,

19:01.100 --> 19:03.705
and I need an A.V. wizard
to be my eyes and ears

19:03.710 --> 19:06.167
for a scenario
I've got going down at 4:00.

19:06.170 --> 19:07.273
[ SMOOCH ]

19:07.280 --> 19:08.907
[ LAUGHS ]

19:08.910 --> 19:10.343
HEY, I'D LOVE TO HELP,

19:10.350 --> 19:13.547
BUT I'VE GOT MY OWN SCENARIO
GOING ON RIGHT HERE.

19:13.550 --> 19:16.474
WALLACE, IF YOU'RE GETTING
ALL THAT JACKIE LOVE

19:16.480 --> 19:17.845
WITH $2 IN YOUR POCKET,

19:17.850 --> 19:22.184
IMAGINE WHAT YOU'D GET
WITH, SAY...$200.

19:22.190 --> 19:24.055
* YEAH *

19:24.060 --> 19:26.927
* I'M HOME FROM WORK... *

19:26.930 --> 19:29.490
YOU DIDN'T ASK HOW HIGH.

19:29.500 --> 19:31.263
WHAT?

19:31.270 --> 19:34.330
DIDN'T GOLDILOCKS
SAY "JUM P"?

19:34.340 --> 19:36.865
IT IS NOT EVEN LIKE THAT.

19:36.870 --> 19:38.167
WHAT'S IT LIKE?

19:38.170 --> 19:39.865
WE'RE FRIENDS, JACKIE.

19:39.870 --> 19:42.873
IF SHE NEEDS ME, I'M GONNA COME
THROUGH, LIKE SHE WOULD FOR ME.

19:42.880 --> 19:45.440
RIGHT. I GUESS YOU HAVE
DIFFERENT RULES HERE.

19:45.450 --> 19:47.077
WHERE I'M FROM,

19:47.080 --> 19:49.674
THE GIRL YOU MAKE OUT WITH
IS THE ONE YOU DO FAVORS FOR.

19:49.680 --> 19:53.810
I MAY HAVE TO HAVE A CHAT
WITH MISS PIXY STICK.

19:53.820 --> 19:56.482
I WOULDN'T DO THAT.

19:56.490 --> 19:59.357
SHE'S NOT SOMEBODY
YOU WANT TO PISS OFF.

19:59.360 --> 20:00.691
* YEAH *

20:00.700 --> 20:02.122
NEITHER AM I.

20:02.130 --> 20:04.223
* JEALOUS LOVE, YEAH *

20:04.230 --> 20:05.561
* AHHHHHH *

20:18.880 --> 20:20.279
[ ENGINE STOPS ]

20:20.280 --> 20:21.941
SORRY I'M LATE.

20:21.950 --> 20:24.714
WHIPPED-CREAM FIGHT
AT THE SORORITY HOUSE.

20:24.720 --> 20:25.539
[ LAUGHS ]

20:25.550 --> 20:27.359
CAN YOU HAND ME A MIC?

20:27.360 --> 20:29.885
YOU GOT SOMEPLACE
TO HIDE IT?

20:29.890 --> 20:31.050
[ LAUGHS ]

20:31.060 --> 20:32.482
DO YOU OWN THOSE CLOTHES

20:32.490 --> 20:35.755
OR DID YOU JUST MAKE A STOP
AT DIRTY-COEDS 'R' US?

20:35.760 --> 20:36.749
HA HA.

20:36.760 --> 20:39.797
AND I NEED TO BE
PAID UP FOR TONIGHT.

20:39.800 --> 20:43.861
[ SIGHS ] GOTTA MAKE
A LITTLE PEACE WITH MY WOMAN.

20:43.870 --> 20:45.861
ARE YOU SURE
SHE'S YOUR WOMAN?

20:45.870 --> 20:48.179
'CAUSE I SAW HER
AT JAVA THE HUT

20:48.180 --> 20:50.273
THE NIGHT
AI-TER OUR DOUBLE DATE,

20:50.280 --> 20:52.077
AND SOME GUY
WAS ALL OVER HER.

20:52.080 --> 20:56.073
LIKE A COUPLE WEEKS AGO,
WHEN WE ONLY HAD LIKE TWO DATES.

20:56.080 --> 20:57.149
SO WHAT?

20:57.150 --> 20:58.845
SO IT'S PROGRESSED?

20:58.850 --> 21:00.488
YEAH. IT'S PROGRESSED.

21:00.490 --> 21:04.153
HAVE YOU SEEN HER
WITH ANOTHER GUY SINCE? NO.

21:04.160 --> 21:05.821
SEE -- WHEN YOU ASSUME,

21:05.830 --> 21:08.856
YOU REALLY JUST
MAKE AN ASS OUT OF YOU.

21:08.860 --> 21:11.499
[ SIGHS ] JUST STAY
AS TIGHT AS YOU CAN.

21:11.500 --> 21:14.958
JUST GO LOLITA HIS ASS.
LET ME DO MY THING.

21:22.310 --> 21:24.608
[ AIR HISSES ]

21:26.510 --> 21:28.478
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

21:31.990 --> 21:33.855
[ Scottish accent]
CAN I HELP YOU WITH SOMETHING?

21:33.860 --> 21:36.351
PLEASE.
THAT WOULD BE SO GREAT.

21:36.360 --> 21:38.555
WAIT.
DO YOU HAVE AN ACCENT?

21:38.560 --> 21:40.755
YEAH, I'M SCOTTISH.

21:40.760 --> 21:42.398
REALLY?

21:42.400 --> 21:45.062
LIKE, FROM SCOTLAND?

21:45.070 --> 21:46.890
[ LAUGHS ]

21:46.900 --> 21:48.162
THAT'S SO AWESOME.

21:48.170 --> 21:52.368
FOREIGN MEN ARE SO MUCH SEXIER
THAN REGULAR MEN.

21:53.210 --> 21:54.802
OH. SORRY.

21:54.810 --> 21:57.643
I HOPE I'M NOT BOTHERING YOU.
IT'S JUST, I GOT A FLAT.

21:57.650 --> 22:00.813
AND MY CELLPHONE'S DEAD,
AND I CAN'T FIND MY AAA CARD.

22:00.820 --> 22:03.311
DO YOU THINK
YOU COULD GIVE ME A HAND?

22:03.320 --> 22:05.880
I TRIED REAL HARD.

22:05.890 --> 22:08.950
I JUST COULDN'T
GET THE NUTS OFF.

22:08.960 --> 22:11.884
I THINK
THEY'RE JUST TOO TIGHT.

22:11.890 --> 22:14.688
BUT I DID JUST PUT LOTION
ALL OVER MY HANDS,

22:14.700 --> 22:16.827
SO THEY'RE
KIND OF SLIPPERY.

22:16.830 --> 22:18.058
[CLANK]

22:18.070 --> 22:21.699
YOU DO KNOW YOU'VE GOT TO JACK
THE CAR UP FIRST, RIGHT?

22:21.700 --> 22:24.601
OH, YEAH.
DO YOU HAVE A JACK?

22:29.980 --> 22:32.198
OH, YOU -- UH...

22:32.210 --> 22:33.768
YOU'VE GOT, UM...

22:33.780 --> 22:34.769
OH.

22:36.050 --> 22:37.688
HOW CUTE ARE YOU.

22:45.930 --> 22:48.023
NO, KEEP IT.

22:48.030 --> 22:51.124
LISTEN -- WE COULD BE OUT HERE
ALL DAY WITH ME DOING THIS.

22:51.130 --> 22:53.792
SO WHY DON'T I GO IN
AND CALL YOU A TOW TRUCK?

22:53.800 --> 22:56.064
DO YOU HAVE A COMPUTER
IN THERE?

22:56.070 --> 22:59.801
BECAUSE I KIND OF NEED
MORE THAN A TOW TRUCK RIGHT NOW.

22:59.810 --> 23:02.301
I GO TO UCSD,
AND I HAVE THIS MIDTERM

23:02.310 --> 23:05.677
THAT, IF I DON'T TURN IN,
IN ABOUT 10 MINUTES...

23:08.020 --> 23:09.874
ALL RIGHT. COME ON.

23:15.690 --> 23:20.525
[ Staticky ] Okay, come on.
The accent?

23:20.530 --> 23:22.725
[ STATIC ]

23:24.970 --> 23:27.689
ARE YOU, LIKE,
THE CATCH OF THE YEAR OR WHAT?

23:27.700 --> 23:29.236
HARDLY.
PLEASE.

23:29.240 --> 23:31.458
[ GASPS ] MY GIRLFRIEND PAIGE
WOULD LOVE THIS PLACE!

23:31.470 --> 23:33.631
SHE'S NOT
MY GIRLFRIEND-GIRLFRIEND.

23:33.640 --> 23:34.971
SHE'S JUST MY FRIEND.

23:34.980 --> 23:37.540
I MEAN, WE SHARE A DORM ROOM,
SO, WHATEVER.

23:37.550 --> 23:39.108
IT'S COLLEGE, RIGHT?

23:39.110 --> 23:42.841
OH, SHE WOULD REALLY LOVE
THIS PLACE.

23:42.850 --> 23:47.458
I MEAN, WHO WOULDN'T WANT
TO WAKE UP TO THIS VIEW?

23:47.460 --> 23:50.782
YOU SHOULD REALLY LET ME KNOW
IF YOU WANT TO PARTY WITH US.

23:50.790 --> 23:52.348
WE'RE FUN --
DOUBLE THE FUN.

23:52.360 --> 23:55.921
I DON'T HAVE TOO MANY PARTIES.
I'M A PRETTY MELLOW GUY.

23:55.930 --> 23:57.329
REALLY?

23:57.330 --> 23:58.695
YOU SEEM KIND OF --

23:58.700 --> 24:00.588
I DON'T KNOW --
WILD TO ME,

24:00.600 --> 24:03.068
LIKE A CAGED ANIMAL
KIND OF THING.

24:03.070 --> 24:06.437
YOU'D HAVE TO ASK MY GIRLFRIEND
ABOUT THAT --

24:06.440 --> 24:07.907
MY ACTUAL GIRLFRIEND.

24:07.910 --> 24:09.798
WE'RE NOT JUST DORM-MATES,
IF YOU GET MY DRIl-T.

24:09.810 --> 24:12.370
[ Staticky ] Veronica:
I bet she's...pretty.

24:12.380 --> 24:13.813
Collin:
Drop. . .gorgeous.

24:13.820 --> 24:15.549
[ SIGHS ]
CAN I ASK YOU SOMETHING?

24:15.550 --> 24:16.619
SURE.

24:16.620 --> 24:18.087
WHAT ABOUT ME?

24:18.090 --> 24:22.151
I MEAN, IF THE RANGE WERE
PRETTY TO DROP-DEAD GORGEOUS,

24:22.160 --> 24:24.321
WHERE WOULD I FALL?

24:24.330 --> 24:26.025
YOU'D FALL UNDER

24:26.030 --> 24:29.989
"KNOWS SHE'S GORGEOUS
BUT LIKES TO HEAR IT ANYWAY."

24:30.000 --> 24:32.662
DON'T FORGET
ABOUT THAT MIDTERM.

24:36.640 --> 24:39.108
[ STATIC ]

24:39.170 --> 24:40.774
VERONICA...

24:44.610 --> 24:47.044
THIS IS REALLY SWEET
OF YOU.

24:47.050 --> 24:50.508
I OWE YOU, LIKE,
THE BIGGEST FAVOR EVER.

24:50.520 --> 24:55.059
SERIOUSLY, YOU CAN ASK ME
FOR ANYTHING.

24:55.060 --> 24:57.051
SOMEBODY'S A BIG MOVIE BUFF,
I SEE.

24:57.060 --> 24:59.051
QUICK -- FAVORITE MOVIE
OF ALL TIME.

24:59.060 --> 25:01.153
DON'T THINK ABOUT IT.
JUST ANSWER.

25:01.160 --> 25:03.196
OH, I DON'T KNOW.
THAT'S A HARD ONE.

25:03.200 --> 25:05.521
THIS REALLY ISN'T MY PLACE,
ACTUALLY.

25:05.530 --> 25:07.634
I'M JUST HOUSESITTING
FOR MY FRIEND.

25:07.640 --> 25:11.667
YOUR FRIEND
A BIG NICOLAS CAGE FAN?

25:11.670 --> 25:13.672
MY FRIEND IS NIC CAGE.

25:13.680 --> 25:16.240
REALLY?

25:19.280 --> 25:20.508
NIC CAGE.

25:20.510 --> 25:21.818
THAT'S HOT.

25:21.820 --> 25:23.811
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

25:23.820 --> 25:25.913
WOULD YOU EXCUSE ME
A SECOND?

25:34.160 --> 25:35.627
HELLO.

25:35.630 --> 25:37.120
UH, HI.

25:39.670 --> 25:42.093
WOULD YOU LIKE
TO HELP THE HUNGRY,

25:42.100 --> 25:44.705
STARVING CHILDREN OF...
THE WORLD?

25:44.710 --> 25:47.804
I'M SORRY --
ARE YOU SELLING SOMETHING?

25:48.680 --> 25:50.705
YES. I AM.

25:50.710 --> 25:54.714
I'M SELLING, UM,
PENS AND...CANDY.

25:54.720 --> 25:57.109
I'LL TAKE A COUPLE OF BOXES
OF CANDY.

26:05.190 --> 26:06.919
ALL I GOT IS THIS BOX.

26:06.930 --> 26:09.728
[ LAUGHS ]
THAT BOX IS OPENED.

26:09.730 --> 26:11.823
YOU WANT A COUPLE PENS?

26:13.200 --> 26:15.259
I E-MAILED THE PAPER
AND CALLED AAA.

26:15.270 --> 26:18.159
THANKS FOR YOUR HELP.
YOUR KARMA'S GOLDEN. CIAO!

26:19.540 --> 26:20.802
Veronica:
Whatcha doin'?

26:20.810 --> 26:22.903
I'M CRAMMING
FOR THAT LATIN QUIZ.

26:22.910 --> 26:25.174
CAN'T FORGET ABOUT
THE KANE LEGACY.

26:25.180 --> 26:26.340
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

26:26.350 --> 26:28.648
Have you had dinner?

26:28.650 --> 26:32.017
NO, I'M TIRED
OF ROOM SERVICE.

26:33.350 --> 26:37.719
THEN MAY I SUGGEST
"DIM SUM AND THEN SOME"?

26:38.690 --> 26:42.148
I GOT THE "DON'T WAIT UP" CALL
FOR THE SECOND NIGHT IN A ROW.

26:42.160 --> 26:45.493
AND IF DAD CAN WORK ALL NIGHT
WITH MRS. FENNEL, THEN...

26:45.500 --> 26:46.899
MMM.

26:48.270 --> 26:51.239
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATION
ON TELEVISION ]

26:54.240 --> 26:56.037
HMM.

26:56.040 --> 26:59.168
WHAT IF WE START THE EVENING
WITH "AND THEN SOME"

26:59.180 --> 27:01.819
AND WORK OUR WAY BACK
TO THE DIM SUM?

27:01.820 --> 27:04.914
IT'S OFFICIALLY
UNDER CONSIDERATION.

27:04.920 --> 27:07.650
CAN I ASK YOU
SOMETHING FIRST?

27:07.660 --> 27:10.254
YES TO COSTUMES.
NO TO PROPS.

27:10.260 --> 27:11.727
DOES THAT COVER IT?

27:11.730 --> 27:13.357
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL ME

27:13.360 --> 27:16.727
HOW OFTEN YOU'D VISITED MEG
SINCE THE ACCIDENT?

27:18.330 --> 27:21.458
CHINESE FOOD IT IS.
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

27:21.470 --> 27:24.030
YOU WANT ONE EGG ROLL
OR TWO?

27:26.210 --> 27:29.077
MENTAL NOTE -- DON'T MENTION
PARTNER'S EX-GIRLFRIEND

27:29.080 --> 27:30.775
IF ONE EXPECTS TO FOOL AROUND.

27:30.780 --> 27:32.270
AND WHILE WE'RE ON THE SUBJECT

27:32.280 --> 27:34.248
OF MEN I FAILED
TO SEDUCE TODAY,

27:34.250 --> 27:36.468
TIME TO SEE
WHAT COLLIN LIKES TO GOOGLE.

27:36.480 --> 27:39.540
WHAT DIRTY SECRETS ARE LURKING
IN YOUR BROWSER HISTORY?

27:39.550 --> 27:44.055
ESCORT AGENCIES? bootycall.com?
NEPTUNE SWINGLES?

27:44.060 --> 27:45.755
WELL, LOOK AT THAT.

27:45.760 --> 27:49.355
JULIE WAS AFRAID TO TELL COLLIN
ABOUT HER FAMILY'S MONEY.

27:49.360 --> 27:52.397
APPARENTLY, HE'S FIGURED
THAT OUT ALL ON HIS OWN.

27:56.740 --> 27:59.402
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

27:59.410 --> 28:01.878
OH, MY GOD.
IT'S MY DAD.

28:04.410 --> 28:05.843
WHO IS IT?

28:05.850 --> 28:09.672
IT'S LIZZIE. UM, I REALLY NEED
TO TALK TO YOU.

28:09.680 --> 28:11.181
H-HANG ON A SEC.

28:11.190 --> 28:14.387
What is Meg's sister
doing here at 2:00 A.M.?

28:21.260 --> 28:22.420
Perfect!

28:22.430 --> 28:25.228
[ SIGHS ]

28:27.700 --> 28:29.133
[ SIGHS ]

28:34.440 --> 28:37.637
SORRY. I DIDN'T KNOW
WHERE ELSE TO GO.

28:37.640 --> 28:39.278
Duncan:
IS MEG ALL RIGHT?

28:39.280 --> 28:41.373
SHE DIDN'T WAKE UP
OR ANYTHING.

28:41.380 --> 28:43.541
MY PARENTS GOT A CALL
FROM THE SCHOOL.

28:43.550 --> 28:46.348
THEY'RE GOING TOMORROW
TO CLEAN OUT MEG'S LOCKER.

28:46.350 --> 28:50.309
SHE KEPT THIS AT SCHOOL.
IT'S GOT EVERYTHING ON IT.

28:50.320 --> 28:51.856
I'M SURE MEG TOLD YOU

28:51.860 --> 28:55.023
THAT MY PARENTS
AREN'T REAL BIG ON PRIVACY.

28:55.030 --> 28:58.818
THEY GO THROUGH OUR ROOMS,
OUR CARS, OUR BACKPACKS.

28:58.830 --> 29:01.037
Duncan: SO YOU WANT ME
TO HIDE IT FOR HER?

29:01.040 --> 29:03.338
WELL, WHATEVER GENIUS
CALLED FROM THE OFFICE

29:03.340 --> 29:05.137
TOLD MY PARENTS
ABOUT THIS COMPUTER.

29:05.140 --> 29:07.233
MEG HAS A LAPTOP
MY PARENTS DIDN'T KNOW ABOUT.

29:07.240 --> 29:09.538
THEY'RE GONNA WANT
TO SEE WHAT'S ON IT.

29:09.540 --> 29:11.041
I DON'T HAVE THE PASSWORD,

29:11.050 --> 29:13.848
BUT WE HAVE TO GET HER
PERSONAL STUFF OFF THIS COMPUTER

29:13.850 --> 29:15.215
AND PUT IT BACK BY MORNING.

29:15.220 --> 29:18.280
OKAY, SO WHAT DO
YOU WANT ME TO DO?

29:18.290 --> 29:20.952
YOU'RE THE SON
OF A COMPUTER VISIONARY.

29:20.960 --> 29:22.552
CAN'T YOU DO SOMETHING?

29:22.560 --> 29:24.653
I CAN BURN A CD.

29:24.660 --> 29:27.322
ALL I KNOW IS IF MY PARENTS
SEE WHAT'S ON THERE,

29:27.330 --> 29:29.423
THEY'LL PULL THE PLUG
ON MEG TOMORROW.

29:29.430 --> 29:31.990
CAN I USE YOUR BATHROOM
REAL QUICK?

29:32.000 --> 29:33.934
UH, UH...
N-NOT REALLY.

29:38.270 --> 29:40.204
HI, LIZZIE.

29:41.910 --> 29:44.902
OKAY, SO, APPARENTLY,
LOOKS REALLY CAN'T KILL.

29:44.910 --> 29:46.446
I'M SORRY.
I DIDN'T WANT --

29:46.450 --> 29:47.701
DID YOU HEAR US?

29:47.710 --> 29:49.439
YES.

29:49.450 --> 29:53.386
AND IF YOU'LL LET ME,
I KNOW SOMEONE WHO CAN HELP.

29:53.390 --> 29:56.780
Mac: I HAVE TO SAY,
IT IS A LITTLE COMFORTING.

29:56.790 --> 30:00.419
I HAVEN'T SNUCK OUT OF MY HOUSE
AT 3:00 AM. IN A WHILE.

30:00.430 --> 30:03.149
NICE TO KNOW
I STILL HAVE THE CHOPS.

30:05.000 --> 30:06.991
AND I'M IN.
THIS IS THE HARD DRIVE.

30:07.000 --> 30:09.764
YOU WANT ALL THE E-MAILS,
RIGHT?

30:09.770 --> 30:10.907
MM-HMM.

30:10.910 --> 30:13.561
YOU MUST HAVE
SOME NOSY-ASS PARENTS.

30:13.570 --> 30:15.299
[ CHUCKLES ]

30:17.740 --> 30:19.503
[ BEEP ]

30:19.510 --> 30:21.569
AND THIS GOES TO YOU?

30:21.580 --> 30:23.548
RIGHT?

30:23.550 --> 30:25.814
YEAH, I GUESS.

30:32.430 --> 30:35.695
ARE YOU CRAZY, DUNCAN,
LEAVING THIS OUT IN THE OPEN?

30:35.700 --> 30:39.921
DO YOU LEAVE HEROIN OUT
WHEN IGGY POP SPENDS THE NIGHT?

30:39.930 --> 30:44.230
* KEEP YOU UP ALL NIGHT IF I *

30:44.240 --> 30:48.108
* TRY TO REMAIN CALM *

30:48.110 --> 30:50.169
* HOW CAN THEY ASK? *

30:50.180 --> 30:51.602
[ BEEP ]

30:51.610 --> 30:55.819
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]
* I WANT THE OCEAN RIGHT NOW *

30:55.820 --> 30:59.881
* I WANT THE OCEAN RIGHT NOW *

30:59.890 --> 31:01.710
HELLO, JULIE.

31:01.720 --> 31:02.982
WAS IT AWFUL?

31:02.990 --> 31:05.788
He was
a consummate gentleman.

31:05.790 --> 31:07.223
HE DIDN'T TRY TO FLIRT.

31:07.230 --> 31:10.495
AND, IN FACT, HE JUST TOLD ME
HOW GREAT YOU WERE.

31:12.470 --> 31:13.869
[ Laughs ] Okay.

31:13.870 --> 31:16.065
I guess this is the moment

31:16.070 --> 31:18.129
that I ofﬁcially became
a jealous freak.

31:18.140 --> 31:20.267
HEY, JULIE,
CAN I CALL YOU BACK LATER?

31:20.270 --> 31:22.500
* I GET SO JEALOUS *

31:23.980 --> 31:27.939
* THAT I CAN'T EVEN WORK *

31:27.950 --> 31:31.909
* THERE I AM IN THE MORNING *

31:31.920 --> 31:35.412
* I DON'T LIKE WHAT I SEE *

31:35.420 --> 31:39.151
* THERE I AM IN THE MORNING *

31:39.160 --> 31:41.128
* I DON'T LIKE WHAT I SEE *

31:41.130 --> 31:44.566
Man:
HE ALREADY LEFT FOR WORK.

31:48.640 --> 31:49.595
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

31:49.600 --> 31:50.828
IT'S LAMB.

31:50.840 --> 31:53.968
I'M THINKING I MIGHT HAVE
A BOOT FOR YOU, TOO.

31:53.980 --> 31:55.777
ANY IDEAS
WHERE I CAN PUT IT?

31:55.780 --> 31:59.568
HEY, YOU STARTED IT WITH YOUR
"I FOUND YOU A WANTED MAN" B.S.

31:59.580 --> 32:02.515
YOU SEND ME IN
TO ARREST CARL MORGAN,

32:02.520 --> 32:04.988
A.K.A. Nathan Woods.

32:06.390 --> 32:07.743
CHICAGO COP.

32:07.750 --> 32:10.457
Big-time
decorated detective.

32:10.460 --> 32:13.054
DID YOU THINK I WOULDN'T
CHECK UP ON THE GUY, KEITH?

32:13.060 --> 32:14.857
HIS RECORD IS
ONE PHONE CALL AWAY.

32:14.860 --> 32:18.318
How stupid do you think
that I am?

32:19.700 --> 32:23.067
I KNOW IT'S AWFUL IF YOU
WOULDN'T TELL ME OVER THE PHONE.

32:32.910 --> 32:35.413
AFTER A THOROUGH
INVESTIGATION,

32:35.420 --> 32:39.186
COLLIN APPEARS TO BE
A LOYAL, COMMITTED PARTNER,

32:39.190 --> 32:41.215
WITHOUT A CRIMINAL RECORD.

32:41.220 --> 32:45.350
AND HIS FRIENDS AND EXES
BOTH SPEAK VERY HIGHLY OF HIM.

32:45.360 --> 32:48.818
THE BAD NEWS
MUST BE REALLY BAD?

32:48.830 --> 32:50.491
THE HOUSE
HE CURRENTLY LIVES IN

32:50.500 --> 32:52.468
AND THE CAR HE DRIVES
AREN'T HIS.

32:52.470 --> 32:55.234
HE'S HOUSESITTING...
FOR NICOLAS CAGE.

32:55.240 --> 32:58.505
THAT'S LISA MARIE
IN THE FRAMED PHOTO ON THE BAR.

32:58.510 --> 33:01.104
AND, FINALLY,
IT APPEARS AS THOUGH

33:01.110 --> 33:04.170
HE DID DO SOME RESEARCH
INTO YOUR BACKGROUND,

33:04.180 --> 33:07.047
AND HE IS AWARE
THAT YOUR FAMILY IS WEALTHY.

33:07.050 --> 33:11.180
[Voice breaking ] HE WENT
DIGGING FOR INFORMATION ON ME?

33:11.190 --> 33:13.249
I SHOULD HAVE KNOWN.

33:13.250 --> 33:15.514
HE TOLD ME
HE HAD A TRUST FUND.

33:15.520 --> 33:18.182
HE TOTALLY LET ME BELIEVE
THAT HOUSE WAS HIS!

33:19.790 --> 33:22.258
I HAVE SOME OF HIS
INTERNET HISTORY ON MY COMPUTER

33:22.260 --> 33:24.069
IF YOU WANT TO --

33:25.130 --> 33:27.928
MR. MARS. ITHOUGHT YOU HAD
THE KIWANIS BANQUET.

33:27.930 --> 33:32.139
MISS BLOCK, I NEED TO SPEAK
WITH VERONICA FOR A MOMENT.

33:32.140 --> 33:34.335
WOULD YOU MIND?

33:34.340 --> 33:35.375
SURE.

33:35.380 --> 33:38.008
I NEED TO GO STAND IN TRAFFIC
FOR A WHILE,

33:38.010 --> 33:40.672
MAYBE JUMP OFF A PIER.

33:46.020 --> 33:48.011
ANOTHER SATISFIED CUSTOMER?

33:48.020 --> 33:50.784
HERE.

33:50.790 --> 33:53.918
CAN YOU FILE THIS UNDER
"CASES I DON'T HAVE TIME FOR

33:53.930 --> 33:57.559
THAT MY DISOBEDIENT DAUGHTER
CAN TAKE BEHIND MY BACK"?

33:57.560 --> 33:58.868
I'M REALLY SORRY.

33:58.870 --> 34:00.121
FOR WHAT?

34:00.130 --> 34:02.166
TAKING THE CASE
OR GETTING CAUGHT?

34:02.170 --> 34:03.797
OKAY, FOR BOTH.

34:03.800 --> 34:06.667
I JUST THOUGHT IT WAS CRAZY
TO PASS UP THAT AMOUNT OF MONEY,

34:06.670 --> 34:08.570
AND I THOUGHT
I COULD HANDLE IT.

34:08.580 --> 34:11.572
YOU ALWAYS THINK
YOU CAN HANDLE IT, VERONICA.

34:11.580 --> 34:15.141
BELIEVE IT OR NOT, AT 18,
YOU CAN'T HANDLE EVERYTHING.

34:15.150 --> 34:18.039
AND YOU DON'T GET AWAY
WITH IT ALL EITHER.

34:18.050 --> 34:19.244
I KNOW.

34:19.250 --> 34:21.480
WHETHER IT'S PLAYING "I SPY"
AFTER SCHOOL

34:21.490 --> 34:24.584
OR STAYING OUT ALL NIGHT
AT YOUR BOYFRIEND'S HOTEL ROOM,

34:24.590 --> 34:29.095
YOU'RE JUST NOT QUITE AS CLEVER
AS YOU THINK YOU ARE.

34:43.880 --> 34:45.609
[ DIALING ]

34:48.320 --> 34:51.619
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

34:53.550 --> 34:54.482
Julie: Hello?

34:54.490 --> 34:56.856
JULIE, I JUST THOUGHT
OF SOMETHING.

34:56.860 --> 35:00.580
YOU KNOW, YOU THINK
YOU'RE DATING PRINCE CHARMING.

35:00.590 --> 35:04.219
BUT YOU'RE REALLY DATING
PRINCE CHARMING'S KATO.

35:04.230 --> 35:05.993
[ Sighs ]

35:06.000 --> 35:08.764
Ijust called him.

35:08.770 --> 35:11.568
I ENDED IT.

35:11.570 --> 35:13.561
IT'S OVER.

35:15.480 --> 35:18.244
AS SOON AS HE CHECKS
HIS MESSAGES.

35:18.250 --> 35:20.639
YOU BROKE UP WITH HIM
ON HIS --

35:20.650 --> 35:24.245
JULIE, THE INTERNET SEARCH
THAT COLLIN DID ON YOUR FAMILY

35:24.250 --> 35:25.842
WAS DATED FIVE DAYS AGO.

35:25.850 --> 35:27.181
YEAH. SO?

35:27.190 --> 35:29.886
So you found the ring
like two weeks ago.

35:29.890 --> 35:32.529
HE CHECKED INTO YOUR FAMILY
AFTER HE BOUGHT THE RING.

35:32.530 --> 35:34.657
HE WAS PROBABLY LOOKING
TO FIND YOUR FATHER

35:34.660 --> 35:36.389
SO HE COULD ASK
FOR HIS APPROVAL.

35:36.400 --> 35:38.789
I'LL BET HE DIDN'T EVEN KNOW
ABOUT THE MONEY.

35:38.800 --> 35:41.268
HE LIED ABOUT THE HOUSE.

35:41.270 --> 35:42.828
HE TOLD YOU IT WAS HIS?

35:42.840 --> 35:46.230
IT WAS IMPLIED. HE PROBABLY LIED
ABOUT THE TRUST FUND, TOO.

35:46.240 --> 35:48.731
YOU DIDN'T EXACTLY TELL HIM
THE TRUTH EITHER.

35:48.740 --> 35:51.800
IT'S ONE THING TO LIE
AND SAY YOU'RE NOT RICH.

35:51.810 --> 35:54.711
THE OTHER WAY AROUND
IS WAY LESS COOL.

35:54.720 --> 35:57.109
I THINK I GET IT NOW.

35:57.120 --> 35:58.985
MONEY MATTERS.

35:58.990 --> 36:01.185
OF COURSE IT MATTERS.

36:02.320 --> 36:04.880
[ TELEPHONE SLAMS ]

36:04.890 --> 36:07.779
ALICIA? ALICIA?

36:07.790 --> 36:10.850
IT'S ME -- KEITH.

36:10.860 --> 36:12.669
ANYBODY HOME?

36:36.320 --> 36:38.379
WHEN YOUR MOM'S AN ALCOHOLIC,

36:38.390 --> 36:41.359
YOU SPEND A LOT OF TIME
LOOKING AT BOTTLES.

36:56.440 --> 36:58.271
"JULIE, I WANTED YOU
TO HAVE THESE.

36:58.280 --> 37:01.272
"EVERYTHING PATRICK COLLIN
NEVIN TOLD YOU WAS TRUE.

37:01.280 --> 37:02.770
"HE DOES HAVE A TRUST FUND --

37:02.780 --> 37:05.146
"PERHAPS BIGGER THAN
EITHER OF US IMAGINED.

37:05.150 --> 37:06.617
"THE ENCLOSED ARTICLE MENTIONS

37:06.620 --> 37:08.349
"THAT HE HATES
TO FLAUNT HIS WEALTH

37:08.360 --> 37:09.588
"OR HIS CELEBRITY FRIENDSHIPS.

37:09.590 --> 37:10.989
"YOU BOTH WANTED TO BE SURE

37:10.990 --> 37:13.857
"YOU WERE LOVED
FOR WHO YOU REALLY WERE.

37:13.860 --> 37:16.749
AND IT SEEMS
THAT ONE OF YOU WAS."

37:20.230 --> 37:22.437
[ TELEPHONE RINGING ]

37:26.970 --> 37:28.972
KEITH MARS.

37:28.980 --> 37:31.403
MR. PASCAL, YES.

37:31.410 --> 37:35.813
UH, I KNOW.
IT'S BEEN A LITTLE BUSY HERE.

37:37.780 --> 37:40.749
UM...

37:40.750 --> 37:42.854
HERE WE GO.

37:42.860 --> 37:44.555
[ SIGHS ]

37:44.560 --> 37:46.118
I'M SORRY, SIR.

37:46.130 --> 37:49.622
IT LOOKS LIKE YOUR WIFE IS,
INDEED, HAVING AN AFFAIR.

37:51.430 --> 37:53.091
YOUR UNCLE?

37:53.100 --> 37:55.534
MISSING PERSONS CASE?

37:55.540 --> 37:59.067
I'M VERY SORRY, SIR.
IT'S A LITTLE FILING MIX-UP.

37:59.070 --> 38:03.473
YOU WERE STUCK INSIDE
MR. PASTORELLI'S FILE.

38:06.980 --> 38:10.370
YOUR UNCLE AL IS ALIVE AND WELL
IN A RETIREMENT HOME IN WAIKIKI

38:10.380 --> 38:12.814
AND, AS FAR AS I KNOW,
COMPLETELY FAITHFUL.

38:12.820 --> 38:14.549
[ CHUCKLES ]

38:14.560 --> 38:16.755
I HAVE HIS NUMBER RIGHT HERE.

38:25.070 --> 38:26.890
[ SIGHS ]

38:29.240 --> 38:31.037
OKAY.

38:31.040 --> 38:34.168
MAYBE I CAN USE YOUR HELP
AROUND THE OFFICE...A BIT.

38:34.170 --> 38:37.628
[ IMITATES TIRES SCREECHING ]
I'M SORRY. COME AGAIN?

38:39.250 --> 38:42.310
YOU'RE NEVER GONNA TELL ME
WHAT HAPPENED TO PROMPT THIS.

38:42.320 --> 38:44.311
NOPE.

38:45.590 --> 38:48.559
NOW, I'M JUST TALKING ABOUT
A LITTLE HELP WITH RESEARCH,

38:48.560 --> 38:49.982
FILING, THE PHONES.

38:49.990 --> 38:51.309
I DO GIVE GOOD PHONE.

38:51.320 --> 38:52.856
JUST A COUPLE DAYS A WEEK.

38:52.860 --> 38:54.828
AND YOU'RE KEEPING YOUR JOB
AT THE HUT.

38:54.830 --> 38:57.719
OF COURSE,
I'LL BE NEEDING A RAISE.

38:57.730 --> 38:59.368
SINCE TALKING TO WEEVIL,

38:59.370 --> 39:01.964
I'VE BEEN DYING TO TRACK DOWN
THIS MYSTERIOUS TIPSTER.

39:01.970 --> 39:04.734
WHO KNOWS IF WEEVIL -- OR
THE TIPSTER, FOR THAT MATTER --

39:04.740 --> 39:06.264
WAS TELLING THE TRUTH.

39:06.270 --> 39:07.760
MAYBE CURLY MORAN WAS PART

39:07.770 --> 39:09.829
OF A PLOT TO RETALIATE
AGAINST A P.C.H.er.

39:09.840 --> 39:12.877
AND MAYBE THAT'S EXACTLY WHAT
SOMEONE WANTS US TO BELIEVE.

39:12.880 --> 39:15.849
THAT CALL COULD'VE COME
FROM ANYWHERE --

39:15.850 --> 39:18.580
A BUSINESS LINE,
A PAY PHONE, OR --

39:18.590 --> 39:21.013
OH, MY GOD.

39:21.020 --> 39:23.011
MEET ME, LIKE, AT 7:00.

39:23.020 --> 39:25.580
[ CHEERLEADERS SHOUTING
IN DISTANCE ]

39:29.100 --> 39:30.328
OKAY.

39:30.330 --> 39:32.662
GOD, I JUST CAN'T TAKE
THE BEGGING.

39:32.670 --> 39:34.365
I'LL RELENT, JUST ONCE.

39:34.370 --> 39:36.895
BUT NO CUDDLING AFTER,

39:36.900 --> 39:39.334
AND I WON'T CALL YOU
IN THE MORNING.

39:39.340 --> 39:40.659
SATURDAY, SEPTEMBER 24th,

39:40.670 --> 39:43.138
THERE WAS A 2-MINUTE
AND 23-SECOND PHONE CALL

39:43.140 --> 39:45.973
ON WEEVIL'S CELLPHONE,
MADE FROM YOUR HOUSE.

39:45.980 --> 39:47.174
THE CALLER CLAIMED

39:47.180 --> 39:49.876
THAT CURLY MORAN WAS RESPONSIBLE
FOR THE BUS CRASH --

39:49.880 --> 39:52.440
THE SAME CURLY MORAN
WHO'S FRIENDS WITH YOUR DAD.

39:52.450 --> 39:54.247
ANY EXPLANATION?

39:54.250 --> 39:55.751
OH, MY DAY IS COMPLETE.

39:55.760 --> 39:58.479
VERONICA MARS
HAS ACCUSED ME OF EVIL.

39:58.490 --> 40:00.526
WHERE TO START?

40:00.530 --> 40:02.521
OH, YES -- WHO THE HELL
IS CURLY MORAN?

40:02.530 --> 40:05.090
AND HOW DO YOU KNOW
HE KNOWS MY DAD?

40:05.100 --> 40:06.658
AND WHAT CONSPIRACY THEORY

40:06.670 --> 40:09.468
HAVE YOU PULLED OUT
OF YOUR ASS THIS TIME?

40:09.470 --> 40:12.507
THE FACT, EVIDENCED BY
THE POSTER IN YOUR HOUSE,

40:12.510 --> 40:15.206
IS THAT CURLY MORAN
WAS THE STUNT COORDINATOR

40:15.210 --> 40:18.941
ON "THE LONG HAUL," STARRING
AARON ECHOLLS, CIRCA 1982.

40:18.950 --> 40:21.100
NOW, SEPTEMBER 24th?

40:21.110 --> 40:24.614
LIKE I HAVE ANY IDEA W--

40:24.620 --> 40:27.316
WAIT. I THINKI DO REMEMBER
THAT NIGHT.

40:27.320 --> 40:31.017
THAT WAS THE NIGHT
OF MY "LIFE'S SHORT" PARTY.

40:31.020 --> 40:32.123
HMM.

40:32.130 --> 40:33.483
OF COURSE.

40:33.490 --> 40:36.823
A GROUP OF LOWER-MIDDLE CLASS
STUDENTS PLUMMET TO THEIR DEATH,

40:36.830 --> 40:38.354
AND THE 09ers THROW A PARTY.

40:38.360 --> 40:40.999
HENCE THE "LIFE'S SHORT" PART.
IT WAS IN THEIR HONOR.

40:41.000 --> 40:43.366
AND IN THE END, IT WASN'T JUST
YOUR SOCIAL BETTERS.

40:43.370 --> 40:47.568
IN FACT, YOUR PAL WEEVIL
AND HIS BIKER BOYS CRASHED IT.

40:47.570 --> 40:50.334
OH, AND, UH...
[ LAUGHS]

40:50.340 --> 40:54.379
LAMB AND A HALF-DOZEN DEPUTIES
CAME BY TO BREAK IT UP...

40:54.380 --> 40:56.245
OR, AT LEAST,
COLLECT THE KEGS.

40:56.250 --> 40:58.684
THERE ARE FIVE NUMBERS
REGISTERED TO YOUR HOUSE.

40:58.690 --> 41:00.840
THIS CALL CAME FROM A NUMBER
I DON'T RECOGNIZE.

41:00.850 --> 41:04.308
GEE WHILLIKERS. IT SOUNDS LIKE
YOU'RE ONTO SOMETHING.

41:04.320 --> 41:06.049
MAYBE THE POOL BOY DID IT.

41:06.060 --> 41:07.186
WELL.

41:15.400 --> 41:16.799
YOU DON'T HAVE ANYTHING?

41:16.800 --> 41:18.904
NOT UNDER "WOODS" EITHER?

